headline: How the Goldman Takeover Rumors Are Shaping Northern Trust’s 2025 Valuation Debate
summary: If you are considering what to do with Northern Trust stock, you are not alone. The name keeps coming up in conversations, sometimes as a steady hand in a volatile market and lately as the subject of some intriguing speculation. In just the last year, Northern Trust shares have soared 33.2%, and those who have been holding for three years have seen a remarkable 73.2% gain. headline: Tesla, Netflix set to report earnings as US-China trade fight turns 'unsustainable': What to watch this week
summary: As investors enters shutdown week three, a US-China trade war, credit gesticulation, and an incoming oil glut are weighing on the market.
